    "created_at": "2015-09-29T06:22:17Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-09-29T06:22:17Z",
    "body": "Got a workaround:\n- get displaySize and create window off-screen\n- capture page and close off-screen window\n\n``` javascript\nvar localScreen = require('screen');\nvar display = localScreen.getPrimaryDisplay().workAreaSize;\n_width = display.width;\n_height = display.height;\n\nif (_window === null) {\n  _window = new browserWindow({\n    x: display.width,\n    y: display.height,\n    width: display.width,\n    height: display.height,\n    resizable: false,\n    'skip-taskbar': true,\n     show: true,\n     'enable-larger-than-screen': true\n  });\n```\n"
  },
